      <title>日本央行上田推迟加息押注，日元下跌 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/yen-weakens-nikkei-futures-climb-after-boj-maintains-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫(Kazuo Ueda)反对近期加息的押注，称很难制定退出计划，日元兑美元下跌1%。]]></description>
